1. *Budućnost* je neizvesna. (The future is uncertain.)
2. *Budućnosti* se treba radovati. (We should be happy about the future.)
3. *Budućnosti* se treba iščekivati. (We should anticipate the future.)
4. *Budućnost* se treba nadati. (We should hope for the future.)
5. *Budućnosti* se treba sećati. (We should remember the future.)